{'id': 32599645, 'body': "Hi Amenadiel, thanks for letting us know that you're unable to add a payment method on your account. We use the IMPS (Immediate Payment Service) bank transfer system as the payment method to transfer funds to your bank account. Most bank accounts can be linked instantly and securely by providing an IFSC (Indian Financial System Code) or branch name when requested. 

For more details, visit: https://help.coinbase.com/en-in/coinbase/getting-started/add-a-payment-method/payment-methods

For further assistance, kindly contact our support team here: https://help.coinbase.com/en/community-support so we can look into this for you. Thanks!", 'modified': '2022-10-16T16:15:56Z'}

